WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.000
Okay, go on with the question and I'll leave you with it.

00:00:04.000 --> 00:00:09.000
Could you tell me what is love?

00:00:12.000 --> 00:00:17.000
Finding the right person and feeling comfortable in their silences but

00:00:17.000 --> 00:00:23.000
enjoying their happiness and their sadnesses as well, being there when they're sad.

00:00:23.000 --> 00:00:28.000
Loving every part of a person, be it good or bad.

00:00:28.000 --> 00:00:30.000
Even the snoring.

